{"data":[{"entities":{"mentions":[{"start":64,"end":73,"username":"kana__ah","id":"1892216888148791296"}]},"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:17.000Z","id":"2037651698924269754","author_id":"735283061873508353","text":"Claude Codeにキーワード突っ込むだけで記事からX投稿まで下書き吐き出してくれるツール作ったってことだよな\n\n(via @kana__ah)","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651698924269754"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:03.000Z","id":"2037651639205544197","author_id":"155369088","text":"Claude Code（AnthropicのAIコーディングツール）を導入したのに、\nチームの生産性が上がっていない。\n\nこの状況に心当たりがあるなら、\n原因はツールではなく「環境設計」にある。\n\nAgentic Engineering（AIエージェントを前提にした開発手法）時代の\nベストプラクティスを11項目フル実装した\nClaude","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651639205544197"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:03:00.000Z","id":"2037651627050672622","author_id":"1694182941486919680","text":"今まで基本AIはChatGPTだけ使って月1000万円まで稼ぐことができたんだけど、さらにパワーアップしていくために遂にClaude Codeをお迎えした。僕の手法にClaude Code加わったら最強なヤツができちゃうんじゃね？\uD83D\uDE0Fゴリゴリやっちゃうよーんww https://t.co/vBM7rn6JFb","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651627050672622"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":131,"end":154,"url":"https://t.co/vBM7rn6JFb","expanded_url":"https://x.com/hiroki_e_0711/status/2037651627050672622/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/vBM7rn6JFb","media_key":"3_2037598461294780416"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:25.000Z","id":"2037651479918530891","author_id":"1912488042725797891","text":"Claude Code v2.1.86、地味だけど「運用側が救われる」アップデートだと思う\uD83D\uDCA1  \nAPIリクエストに `X-Claude-Code-Session-Id` が付くようになって、プロキシやゲートウェイでボディ覗かずにセッション単位の集計ができる。これ、監査・課金・障害解析の設計が一段ラクになるやつ。 https://t.co/3wySTWfBYo","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651479918530891"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":158,"end":181,"url":"https://t.co/3wySTWfBYo","expanded_url":"https://x.com/NANDS_AI/status/2037651479918530891/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/3wySTWfBYo","media_key":"3_2037651421634740224"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:00.000Z","id":"2037651375362904467","author_id":"1070650761732796417","text":"Claude Codeのスキル、今日また新しいの入れてみたんだけど、気づいたら「作業する時間」より「何を任せるか考える時間」のほうが長くなってた。\nこれって退化してるのか進化してるのかわからなくなってきた。\n\nでも多分、こっちが本来の使い方なんだよな。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651375362904467"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:02:00.000Z","id":"2037651375161815547","author_id":"1849726211808952320","text":"セミナーに参加して、Claude Codeが気になりすぎて…\n気づいたら課金していました\uD83D\uDE06\n#クラウドタウン https://t.co/cnc182Cgr7","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651375161815547"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":55,"end":78,"url":"https://t.co/cnc182Cgr7","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/crowd_town/status/2036986157213601859","display_url":"x.com/crowd_town/sta…"}],"hashtags":[{"start":46,"end":54,"tag":"クラウドタウン"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:45.000Z","id":"2037651313249644616","author_id":"126853543","text":"\"米AWSがClaude Codeなどデプロイ自動化ツール「Agent Plugins for AWS」を公開\" - ビジネス＋IT #SmartNews  https://t.co/yh3ZQjZLmV","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651313249644616"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":79,"end":102,"url":"https://t.co/yh3ZQjZLmV","expanded_url":"https://l.smartnews.com/m-7q2iw6T6/bs89gZ","display_url":"l.smartnews.com/m-7q2iw6T6/bs8…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037651355935055872/q0Hj7kIN?format=png&name=orig","width":1024,"height":537},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037651355935055872/q0Hj7kIN?format=png&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"米AWSがClaude Codeなどデプロイ自動化ツール「Agent Plugins for AWS」を公開 (ビジネス＋IT)","description":"米Amazon Web ServicesはAIエージェントのClaude CodeやCursorにクラウド環境の設計からデプロイまでの機能を組み込む拡張ツールAgent Plugins for AWSを公開した。開発者がチャットで指示を出すだけでソースコードの解析やインフラ構成の推奨およびコスト見積もりから実際の...","unwound_url":"https://www.smartnews.com/ja-jp/article/4928238734572267782?placement=article-preview-social&utm_campaign=sn_lid%3A4928238734572267782%7Csn_channel%3Acr_ja_top&utm_source=share_ios_twitter&share_id=bs89gZ"}],"hashtags":[{"start":67,"end":77,"tag":"SmartNews"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:30.000Z","id":"2037651251794759687","author_id":"4720427994","text":"最近 Claude Codeのhooks関連を色々触りたいなぁって思っていて、そんな中ifフィールドがサポートされた。これは面白そう。 https://t.co/JvQSE3vwGt","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651251794759687"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":68,"end":91,"url":"https://t.co/JvQSE3vwGt","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/lydiahallie/status/2037573738670297583","display_url":"x.com/lydiahallie/st…"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:01:00.000Z","id":"2037651123759141010","author_id":"1348112411014823938","text":"土曜日の朝\uD83C\uDF1E\n\n今日はエージェント型AI\nClaude Codeを使い倒す日にする\uD83D\uDCAA\n\n昨日2時間でデイトラ尾道を\nAIに作ってもらったけど\nまだまだ使いこなせてない\uD83D\uDE33\n\n午前中はこのエージェントを\n徹底的に使いこなす✊\uD83D\uDD25\n\nそして午後はAmazonプライムで\nギャラクシーエンジェル見ながら\nビール\uD83C\uDF7A","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":9},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037651123759141010"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:21.000Z","id":"2037650959556542910","author_id":"107830304","text":"\uD83D\uDCF0 自分で読む為のAIニュース [1-10/35]\n========================================\n\n1. 週刊AIニュース #2026-03-27 - hotchpotch著\n\uD83D\uDCCE https://t.co/bE69CVzmWL\n\n2. Wikipediaが記事作成におけるAIの使用を取り締まる | TechCrunch\n\uD83D\uDCCE https://t.co/Eh1clgv884\n\n3. Claude CodeとDevinをFour","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650959556542910"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":108,"end":131,"url":"https://t.co/bE69CVzmWL","expanded_url":"https://ainewsdev.substack.com/p/weekly-ai-news-2026-03-27","display_url":"ainewsdev.substack.com/p/weekly-ai-ne…","status":200,"title":"Weekly AI News #2026-03-27","description":"生成系の動向と組織運用の変革を総括する報告書的展望と実務示唆","unwound_url":"https://ainewsdev.substack.com/p/weekly-ai-news-2026-03-27"},{"start":181,"end":204,"url":"https://t.co/Eh1clgv884","expanded_url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wikipedia-cracks-down-on-the-use-of-ai-in-article-writing/","display_url":"techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wik…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037286373804453888/hztPX4FD?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":800},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037286373804453888/hztPX4FD?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Wikipedia cracks down on the use of AI in article writing | TechCrunch","description":"The site, whose policies are subject to change, has struggled with the issue of AI-generated writing.","unwound_url":"https://techcrunch.com/2026/03/26/wikipedia-cracks-down-on-the-use-of-ai-in-article-writing/"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:12.000Z","id":"2037650921476510187","author_id":"2003275986037846016","text":"2026年3月時点のAI開発ツール選び方。\n\nターミナル派 → Claude Code\nIDE統合派 → Cursor\nGitHub中心 → Copilot\n全自動がいい → Devin\n無料で試したい → Windsurf（SWE-1.5が3ヶ月無料）\n\n正解は「1つに絞る」ことじゃない。\n用途で使い分けるのが最強。\n\n僕はClaude Code + Cursorの二刀流。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650921476510187"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:02.000Z","id":"2037650880342933990","author_id":"1694821393068924930","text":"Claudeにやらせてみた\uD83D\uDC40\nブクマ推奨\n\nClaude Codeに「動画作って」と言ったら、\n本当に動画が出てきた。\n\nRemotion Skillsという仕組みで、\nReactベースのコードをClaude Codeが自動生成、\nそのまま動画としてレンダリングされる。\n\nコードは1行も書いてない。 https://t.co/WTDUtYwa8R","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650880342933990"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":151,"end":174,"url":"https://t.co/WTDUtYwa8R","expanded_url":"https://x.com/shinmomo0512/status/2037650880342933990/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/WTDUtYwa8R","media_key":"3_2037620042037383168"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:01.000Z","id":"2037650875632722077","author_id":"1158064998255480832","text":"これ知らずにAGENTS.mdを書いてた人、今すぐ確認しろ。Claude Codeが自動で読むのはCLAUDE.mdだけだ。AGENTS.mdを参照させたいなら@`Importで明示的に取り込む必要がある。ルールを書いても届いていない状態で仕事させてたかもしれない。今日から変わる。 https://t.co/TcsOYxADwQ","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":11},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650875632722077"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":142,"end":165,"url":"https://t.co/TcsOYxADwQ","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/oikon48/status/2037486034087485636","display_url":"x.com/oikon48/status…"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T22:00:00.000Z","id":"2037650872466076028","author_id":"2015836209730535424","text":"Claude Code、ターミナルで\"claude\"って打つだけでAIペアプログラマーが起動する。\n\nCursorみたいにエディタ切り替え不要。既存のワークフローに乗せられるのが強い。\n\nCLAUDE.mdにプロジェクトルール書いておけば、毎回「TypeScriptで書いて」とか言わなくていい。設定ファイル1つで精度が激変する。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650872466076028"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:58:54.000Z","id":"2037650594203386367","author_id":"2004877129335611392","text":"Claude CodeというDAWソフト(笑)はとっても楽しいです\uD83D\uDE0A","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650594203386367"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:58:30.000Z","id":"2037650494039138409","author_id":"3185596082","text":"デザインが明らかにClaude Codeなフィッシングメールが届いた\n見た目は現代的でいいんだけど","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650494039138409"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:56:41.000Z","id":"2037650038692917432","author_id":"1176768396668465152","text":"Claude Codeを使っている人は全員これを読んだ方がいい！\n\nみたいな記事正直今は1ミリも理解できないから興味ないけど、これ全部Obsidianに clippingしておけば、将来の自分が助かるのかもしれないし、不要でもかかる労力はワンポチだけだしーー","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":17},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037650038692917432"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:56:22.000Z","id":"2037649956669170096","author_id":"1872272587738529792","text":"Claude Codeエージェント用のオープンソースUI。Animal Crossing風UX、iMessage連携、組み込みブラウザ、スケジューリング、トンネル機能、拡張、リクエスト自動承認。 https://t.co/EbK8ersa7I","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":7},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649956669170096"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":98,"end":121,"url":"https://t.co/EbK8ersa7I","expanded_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47545642","display_url":"news.ycombinator.com/item?id=475456…","status":200,"title":"Show HN: Open-Source Animal Crossing–Style UI for Claude Code Agents | Hacker News","description":"We posted here on Monday and got some great feedback. We’ve implemented a few of the most requested updates: - iMessage channel support (agents can text people and you c an text agents) Other channels are simple to extend. - A built-in browser (agents can navigate and interact with websites) - Scheduling (run tasks on a timer / cron / in the future) - Built in tunneling so that the agents can share local stuff with you over the internet - More robust MCP and Skills support so anyone can extend it - Auto","unwound_url":"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47545642"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:55:48.000Z","id":"2037649814675149069","author_id":"2024758355567529989","text":"\uD83C\uDD95 Claude Code v2.1.86 リリース！\n\n\uD83D\uDCCC 主な変更点:\n• API リクエストに X-Claude-Code-Session-Id ヘッダーを追加\n• Jujutsu/Sapling の VCS メタデータを除外対象に追加\n• --resume 時のツールID関連エラーを修正\n• Windows での設定ファイル破損問題を修正\n•","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649814675149069"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:51.000Z","id":"2037649575687999549","author_id":"1292995835966312448","text":"【 Claude Code の設計手法 】\n\n私は毎週、PCのフォルダやClaude Code関連のファイル構造をClaude Codeに改善してもらっています。\n\n昨日は、ハーネス設計を導入。実際にどう変わったか？詳しく記事に書きました。設定ファイルの一部も公開しています。 https://t.co/n5gVWK45B1","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":2,"impression_count":179},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649575687999549"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":139,"end":162,"url":"https://t.co/n5gVWK45B1","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/kawai_design/status/2037520290474025416","display_url":"x.com/kawai_design/s…"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:50.000Z","id":"2037649574245052601","author_id":"1894723460812935168","text":"何度でも言います。\nChatGPTだけで全部こなそうとしてる人、\n2026年はかなり苦しくなると思う。\n\n実際に結果出してる人を見てると、\nちゃんと使い分けてるんよね↓\n\n・ネタ・アイデア出し　→ Gemini\n・文章・記事をつくる　→ Claude\n・ツール作成・自動化　→ Claude Code\n・最新情報のリサーチ　→","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":2,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":7},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649574245052601"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:00.000Z","id":"2037649361878839397","author_id":"1292995835966312448","text":"Anthropicが公式で\n「ハーネス設計」の記事を出した。\n\n↓ 核心はこれ\n\n「AIは自分の成果物を評価すると甘くなる。\nだから作る役と評価する役を分けろ」\n\nこれを自分のClaude Codeに\n実装してみました。\n\n↓やったこと\n\n・HTMLを書いた瞬間にPlaywrightで\n　自動スクショ→検証するHook","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":89},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649361878839397"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:54:00.000Z","id":"2037649361669066989","author_id":"1789633726974201856","text":"Claude codeとgeminiで\n\nKindle出版、初めてやってみた。\n\n画像生成→台本→製本→アップロード。一通りの流れを把握するのに丸2日かかった。\n\nでも2冊目からは企画リサーチに時間を割ける。\n\n「1回目は遅くていい。全体を知ることが目的」って自分に言い聞かせてる。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037649361669066989"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:52:23.000Z","id":"2037648954683515118","author_id":"899215053194264576","text":"ビジネスのアイデアが湧く人ほど実行が追いつかない。Claude Codeは100万トークン＝原稿用紙2,500枚分を一度に理解する。競合は数十枚。アイデアが枯渇する人は情報量が足りない。これで差がつく。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037648954683515118"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:50:17.000Z","id":"2037648429288173923","author_id":"1345093696270733313","text":"Claude Code使い始めて、常に頭の片隅に「簡単なプログラムなら作った方が早いのでは？」が選択肢として存在していて、一度人をあやめたことがあるやつみたいになってる。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":10},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037648429288173923"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:49:18.000Z","id":"2037648178905018767","author_id":"1808841669636497408","text":"Claude CodeはCLAUDE.mdだけでも便利ですが、それだけだと「守ってほしいルール」が抜けることがあります。\n\nそこで重要なのがHooksです。\n\nHooksは、Claudeのツール実行前後や終了時などのタイミングで、決めた処理を自動で必ず実行できる仕組みです。たとえば、 https://t.co/Y1auUDUNkE","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":1,"impression_count":82},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037648178905018767"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":143,"end":166,"url":"https://t.co/Y1auUDUNkE","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/akshay_pachaar/status/2037523396876173783","display_url":"x.com/akshay_pachaar…"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:46:22.000Z","id":"2037647439977685305","author_id":"143912702","text":"Claude Code完全攻略マニュアル（2万字超）を更新しました。その後書いた「全体像」「安全設定」「Skill」「Chrome操作」の深堀り記事へのリンクを追記。読み返すたびに次に進める構成になりました。プロフのnoteリンクからどうぞ。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":13},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037647439977685305"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:45:03.000Z","id":"2037647112763322618","author_id":"98082616","text":"ここ数週間かけてClaude CoworkでもClaude Codeでもツール開発やってみてるけど、自分的には今のところCoworkが安心で使いやすい。\n\nそのうちCodeでやることも想像できるけど、Coworkの方が「これをやりますよ」という確認が理解の範疇で安心。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":65},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037647112763322618"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:43:31.000Z","id":"2037646724060311868","author_id":"111904771","text":"claude codeはちょっとした作業をするときに内部でpythonスクリプトを作って対処するの見かけるからこういうの怖いな。\n今攻撃者はやりたい放題になってるのじゃないかな。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":31},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646724060311868"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:43:03.000Z","id":"2037646608947609712","author_id":"1066604502856327169","text":"\"Claude Codeでグロース業務をPO1人で回せるようになった。考え方と気づき\" https://t.co/QSqkdEgZaN","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":15},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646608947609712"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":44,"end":67,"url":"https://t.co/QSqkdEgZaN","expanded_url":"https://l.smartnews.com/m-7qeZtAA0/JCgdoW","display_url":"l.smartnews.com/m-7qeZtAA0/JCg…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037646609992052736/jZRMJ2dP?format=png&name=orig","width":1020,"height":536},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037646609992052736/jZRMJ2dP?format=png&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Claude Codeでグロース業務をPO1人で回せるようになった。考え方と気づき (note（ノート）)","description":"こんにちは。クラシル株式会社 小川です。 ここ数週間、売上分析から施策立案、MAツールへの配信設定、効果検証まで、グロース業務をClaude Codeで自動化する取り組みをしています。 マルチエージェントを活用することで、もともと複数人で分担していた作業が、1人＋AIチームで回りつつあります。 まだ発展途上ですが...","unwound_url":"https://www.smartnews.com/ja-jp/article/4928406307850956255?placement=article-preview-social&utm_source=share_android_other&utm_campaign=sn_lid%3A4928406307850956255%7Csn_channel%3Acr_ja_technology_artificial_intelligence&share_id=JCgdoW"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:42:22.000Z","id":"2037646435043463670","author_id":"2032701494802399232","text":"この使い分け、すごく合理的。\n\n当直中にClaude Codeで文献検索や症例まとめを走らせておいて、\n朝には結果が出てる運用ができたら最高だなと思った。\n臨床しながらバックグラウンドでAIが動いてくれる環境、早く作りたい。 https://t.co/Ukd6zxXxF6","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":18},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646435043463670"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":113,"end":136,"url":"https://t.co/Ukd6zxXxF6","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/fuyutomiyake/status/2036657307271262254","display_url":"x.com/fuyutomiyake/s…"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:41:56.000Z","id":"2037646326264168704","author_id":"1924626975601393668","text":"新着Unity記事！\n『Claude Code × unity-mcp でゲーム開発の企画→公開をワークフロー化した話』\nby -umezu_y-\n#Unity #Qiita\nhttps://t.co/qSOaPasC9R","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":5},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646326264168704"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":88,"end":111,"url":"https://t.co/qSOaPasC9R","expanded_url":"https://qiita.com/umezu_y/items/090a0fd25f9f915ad375","display_url":"qiita.com/umezu_y/items/…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2035552959648669696/2eUEy_xg?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":630},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2035552959648669696/2eUEy_xg?format=jpg&name=150x150","width":150,"height":150}],"status":200,"title":"Claude Code × unity-mcp でゲーム開発の企画→公開をワークフロー化した話 - Qiita","description":"はじめに ChatGPT や Claude に「ブロック崩しを作って」と頼めば、HTML + JavaScript のゲームがすぐに出てくる時代になりました。手軽で楽しいのですが、「やっぱり使い慣れた Unity で作りたい」と思ったことはないでしょうか。 私もその一人で...","unwound_url":"https://qiita.com/umezu_y/items/090a0fd25f9f915ad375"}],"hashtags":[{"start":74,"end":80,"tag":"Unity"},{"start":81,"end":87,"tag":"Qiita"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:41:52.000Z","id":"2037646311055646806","author_id":"1055768748","text":"くそう\n起きて思い付いたアイデアをClaude Codeに壁打ちしたいと思ったら、利用枠上限張り付きでどもならん\n追い課金はもう嫌じゃぁT_T","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":8},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646311055646806"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:40:45.000Z","id":"2037646028909023395","author_id":"1486905432929345536","text":"gemini解約してGoogle cloudに乗り換えた\n\nやっぱAPIでgemini 3.1 imageを呼び出しせるようにすればclaude codeから使えるから便利","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":118},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037646028909023395"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:38:27.000Z","id":"2037645450694836633","author_id":"1469084304","text":"非エンジニアの僕が、Claude Codeだけでアプリを2つリリースした話。\n\nプログラミング経験ゼロ。\nコードは1行も書けない。\n\nそれでも、App Storeにアプリが並んでいる。\n\nDaxFocus（ポモドーロタイマー）\nBindex（手帳アプリ）\n\nどちらもClaude","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":4},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037645450694836633"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:33:23.000Z","id":"2037644174024179757","author_id":"2037601024186216450","text":"【非エンジニア必見】Claude Codeはプログラミング知識ゼロでも使えます。\n\n文系40代がアプリを4日で完成させた事例も。Web版ならブラウザだけでOK。\n\n詳しくはnoteで解説中\uD83D\uDC47\nhttps://t.co/yRgktpg1TL\n\n#ClaudeCode #非エンジニア #バイブコーディング","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037644174024179757"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":96,"end":119,"url