30204"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:30:20.000Z","id":"2037643407108247655","author_id":"1009489992731668480","text":"\uD83C\uDF89 Claude Code × Remotionで「数学の動く教材」が作れた！\n\n「2次関数と動点Pの問題」のモーション動画を、Claude Codeで一発生成。\n\n【やったこと】\n①Claude Codeに「Remotionで2次関数の動点P動画を作って」と指示\n②プロジェクト作成→コンポーネント実装→ビルドまで自動 https://t.co/SPRBy0h5gL","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":29},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037643407108247655"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":161,"end":184,"url":"https://t.co/SPRBy0h5gL","expanded_url":"https://x.com/tekitoo_T_cher/status/2037643407108247655/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/SPRBy0h5gL","media_key":"13_2037643354780123136"}]}},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:30:00.000Z","id":"2037643323310035327","author_id":"1392809566904016901","text":"「AIに情報を渡すのが怖い」って言う人、正直めちゃくちゃ多い。でも47件支援してきて思うのは、怖がって手作業を続けてるほうがよっぽどリスク高い。人はルールを忘れる。疲れたらミスる。Claude Codeは設定ファイルに書いたルールを人よりずっと確実に守る。","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":1,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":6},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037643323310035327"]},{"created_at":"2026-03-27T21:29:10.000Z","id":"2037643111925424620","author_id":"2035541856319385601","text":"Claude Code v2.1.84 がリリース\uD83D\uDE80 Windows向けPowerShellツール（プレビュー）追加、MCP改善、多数のバグ修正など盛りだくさんの更新です。詳細はブログをチェック\uD83D\uDC47 https://t.co/y4UAqVFrDp #ClaudeCode #Anthropic","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":0,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":0},"edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037643111925424620"],"entities":{"urls":[{"start":99,"end":122,"url":"https://t.co/y4UAqVFrDp","expanded_url":"https://algo-kun.hatenablog.com/entry/2026/03/28/062909","display_url":"algo-kun.hatenablog.com/entry/2026/03/…","images":[{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037643154996789248/_7zRoWxo?format=jpg&name=orig","width":1200,"height":630},{"url":"https://pbs.twimg.com/news_img/2037643154996789248/_7zRoWxo?format